ing: 1 (10.75 ounce) can condensed cream of mushroom soup
6 slices American processed cheese, cut into 1-inch pieces
des: "Cheesy chicken recipe that uses only 4 ingredients, practically cooks by itself and makes its own gravy!"
ins: In a large skillet, brown chicken on both sides. In the meantime, in a medium bowl combine the soup, milk and cheese. Mix together. When chicken is browned, pour mixture over chicken pieces. Cook over medium low heat until chicken is done and juices run clear. Serve.
